   *   Ask the Customer Care Center (CCC)

   For questions concerning the U.S. Mint, coins, and Numismatics
   products, please call our Customer Care Center at (800) USA-MINT
   (800-872-6468), from 8:30 a.m. to 5:30 p.m. Eastern Time, Monday -
   Friday.

   You may also contact our Customer Care Center by writing us at:

     U.S. Mint
     Customer Care Center
     Lanham, Maryland 20706-4331

   The U.S. Mint Web Catalog is currently designed to accept orders only
   from the United States, U.S. Territories & Possessions, and U.S.
   Military Post Offices.  At this time, International Orders cannot be
   placed through the U.S. Mint's Web Catalog.  However, the U.S. Mint has
   approximately 15 official International distributors who may assist you
   in acquiring any U.S. Mint numismatic items you desire.  To obtain the
   name and address of a distributor in your country, please write to the
   U.S. Mint's International Division at 801 9th Street, N.W., Washington
   DC 20220, USA or send a fax to (202) 756-6585.

